abstract.gco:CharacterString: Village boundaries of Bihar linked to Census 2001. Map includes data for 45507 villages,134 towns,37 districts and 1 state. This layer is part of the Village Map of India which includes socio-demographic and economic Census data for 2001 at the Village level.
